        <abstract> 
<p>The <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi> attacks THH’s lecture.</p> 
            <p>Assures CD he spoke more favourably of his doctrines than the reports show.</p> 
<p>Agrees with CD’s arguments on sterility of hybrids and predicts physiological experiments will produce physiological species sterile <hi rend="italic">inter se</hi>. Has come even closer to CD’s view especially since <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> paper. Will soon be more Darwinian than CD.</p> 
        </abstract>
